


{"id":2784,"date":"2021-05-15T20:59:23","date_gmt":"2021-05-15T19:59:23","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/?page_id=2784"},"modified":"2025-05-01T23:33:09","modified_gmt":"2025-05-01T22:33:09","slug":"opravy-diagnostika-plneni-klimatizaci","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/opravy-diagnostika-plneni-klimatizaci\/","title":{"rendered":"Klimatizace &#8211; diagnostika, pln\u011bn\u00ed, \u010di\u0161t\u011bn\u00ed klimatizace"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"mp-row-fluid motopress-row mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\"> <div class=\"motopress-clmn mp-span6  mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\">\r\n<p>Klimatizace je b\u011b\u017enou sou\u010d\u00e1st\u00ed v\u011bt\u0161iny modern\u00edch voz\u016f. Pokud, ale nefunguje spr\u00e1vn\u011b, m\u016f\u017ee krom\u011b \u0161patn\u00e9 regulace teploty b\u00fdt tak\u00e9 p\u0159\u00ed\u010dinou zdravotn\u00edch obt\u00ed\u017e\u00ed. M\u00e1te pocit, \u017ee va\u0161e klimatizace v posledn\u00ed dob\u011b m\u00e1lo chlad\u00ed, je hlu\u010dn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed, nebo c\u00edt\u00edte nezvykl\u00fd z\u00e1pach ? Nepodce\u0148ujte situaci a nechte ji zkontrolovat odborn\u00edky<\/p>\r\n<h3 class=\"article_header\"><strong>Servis klimatizace<\/strong><\/h3>\r\n<p>Kompletn\u00ed servis klimatizace (\u00a0 diagnostika, opravy, pln\u011bn\u00ed, \u010di\u0161t\u011bn\u00ed ) . Za hodinu u\u017e m\u016f\u017eete b\u00fdt znovu na cest\u011b a u\u017e\u00edvat si \u010dist\u00e9ho vzduchu ve voze.<\/p>\r\n<h3 class=\"article_header\"><strong>Diagnostick\u00e1 kontrola klimatizace<\/strong><\/h3>\r\n<p>Pomoc\u00ed origin\u00e1ln\u00edch p\u0159\u00edstroj\u016f koncernu <strong>Volkswagen Group<\/strong>\u00a0 \u00a0provedeme kontrolu tlaku chladic\u00edho m\u00e9dia, kontrolu funkce kompresoru i t\u011bsnosti okruhu. Lokalizujeme p\u0159\u00edpadn\u00e9 \u00faniky.<\/p>\r\n<h3 class=\"article_header\"><strong>Opravy klimatizace<\/strong><\/h3>\r\n<p>Pokud diagnostick\u00e1 kontrola odhal\u00ed z\u00e1vadu klimatizace, nemus\u00edte m\u00edt strach. A\u0165 u\u017e se jedn\u00e1 o \u00fanik chladic\u00edho m\u00e9dia, nebo vadn\u00fd kompresor. P\u0159\u00edpadn\u00fd \u00fanik zji\u0161\u0165ujeme pomoc\u00ed nejmodern\u011bj\u0161\u00edch technologi\u00ed (<strong> vod\u00edk<\/strong>, <strong>dus\u00edk<\/strong> ) Opravy n\u00edzkotlak\u00e9ho a vysokotlak\u00e9ho okruhu prov\u00e1d\u00edme pomoc\u00ed\u00a0 za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed pro opravu klimatizac\u00ed <strong>Vulkan Lokring ( neplat\u00ed pro CO2\u00a0 )<\/strong>\u00a0Na\u0161i technici zajist\u00ed rychlou opravu.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n<h3 class=\"article_header\"><strong>Pln\u011bn\u00ed klimatizace<\/strong><\/h3>\r\n<p>V sou\u010dasn\u00e9 dob\u011b se pro servis klimatizace pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 speci\u00e1ln\u00ed ods\u00e1vac\u00ed a pln\u00edc\u00ed stanice. Ty zaji\u0161\u0165uj\u00ed nejen bez\u00fanikovou manipulaci s chladivem ( <strong>R 134 a, HFO 1234 yf, CO2<\/strong> ) , ale tak\u00e9 p\u0159esn\u00e9 pln\u011bn\u00ed p\u0159edepsan\u00e9ho mno\u017estv\u00ed chladiva do okruhu klimatizace<\/p>\r\n<h3 class=\"article_header\"><strong>\u010ci\u0161t\u011bn\u00ed a dezinfekce klimatizace<\/strong><\/h3>\r\n<p>\u010ci\u0161t\u011bn\u00ed a dezinfekci klimatizace prov\u00e1d\u00edme : p\u011bnov\u00fdm \u010disti\u010dem, biocidn\u00edm dezinfek\u010dn\u00edm p\u0159\u00edpravkem ( sprej ), oz\u00f3nem (doporu\u010dujeme )<\/p>\r\n<\/div> <div class=\"motopress-clmn mp-span6  mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\"> <div class=\"motopress-image-obj motopress-text-align-left\"><img src=\"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/klimatizace.jpg\" title=\"klimatizace\" alt=\"klimatizace\" class=\"motopress-image-obj-basic mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right mpce-dsbl-margin-top mpce-dsbl-margin-bottom\" \/><\/div> <\/div> <\/div> <div class=\"mp-row-fluid motopress-row mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\"> <div class=\"